                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 837.001M52/7.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">American Minister</gloss> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Habana</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1913-05-15">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 15, 1913</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>In the absence of instructions on the subject, Mr. Gibson will go to Key West to
                    confer with the Special Representatives on the details of the mission, to
                    expedite definite arrangements on arrival.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Beaupré</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
